{"tid":907080,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"（童年回憶）有冇人睇過至Net奇兵(Code Lyoko)？","createTime":"2018-11-18T13:43:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-04T17:55:31.000Z","uid":222757,"like":43,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"952b4e03d6e9761ecb92e3499889383b2f44ded3","tid":907080,"uid":222757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T13:43:32.000Z","msg":"以前小學雞必睇卡通之一<br />\n一放學番屋企打開放學ICU就有得睇<br />\n首主題曲又勁好聽<br />\n十幾年前已經勁識玩 已經有concept喺2D同3D世界之間穿來穿去 根本走得勁前<br />\n仲早過阿凡達出世多多聲<br />\n<br />\n主角入面最鍾意治狼<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LoVysZE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLoVysZE.png&h=a7ba7f11&s={SIZE}\" />揸住兩碌武士刀又型又靚仔<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fa2pzE6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFa2pzE6.jpg&h=0f5cf8cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n平時仲識搞下GAG又識揸電單車 根本咩女都比佢溝哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VSM2mrG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVSM2mrG.jpg&h=39e984e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n至於點解最唔鐘意傑理明吖明仔大家睇圖都明啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jPAnmjc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjPAnmjc.jpg&h=188ab318&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9aSQvkz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9aSQvkz.jpg&h=697fe111&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oTVRZhc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoTVRZhc.jpg&h=a2b9db8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一個精通電腦同數理嘅單身狗 再加埋副襯到絕嘅眼鏡 從來只係鍵盤同電腦面前默默付出 其實冇人記得佢做過啲咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n先唔講佢連虛擬世界角色都冇 基本上入咗虛擬世界明仔嘅鏡頭唔會多過5秒 淨係得番佢把聲聽下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n根本就係毒撚IT狗連登仔三合一嘅先驅<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/poison.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n而家是但一樣都玩撚完 比人睇唔起 但三樣都齊既明仔居然係十幾年前已經出現咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過做鍵盤戰士㩒幾個制send吓裝備同車 睇吓地圖觀吓星然後通個水其實個個都做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其他人係入面打生打死佢就係到食花生鬼咁死他條（雖然我記得佢係現實坐係個mon面前都成日比個Boss搞鳩佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）計我話根本明仔就最少貢獻 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n所以我細細個已經諗好咗要做另一個治狼 人生大贏家 女又食哂 傻西瓜先會變到明仔咁<br />\n不過小弟又點估到十幾年後自己都變左第二個明仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0edbbe8a05a8cddc04470dbd103269cc9d0acd4a","tid":907080,"uid":142378,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T13:52:12.000Z","msg":"Here we are, going far<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbf265b4819e0ccee8ff481069a92bb58df3d39d","tid":907080,"uid":39249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T13:52:49.000Z","msg":"細個好鍾意睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知而家邊度有得睇返"},{"pid":"f33a8c82748417551e667092cc7329f76f9cdf17","tid":907080,"uid":11544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0edbbe8a05a8cddc04470dbd103269cc9d0acd4a","tid":907080,"uid":142378,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T13:52:12.000Z","msg":"Here we are, going far<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T14:14:10.000Z","msg":"to save all that we love<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"